<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00100</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT INSTITUTING ABSOLUTE DIVORCE AND DISSOLUTION OF MARRIAGE IN THE PHILIPPINES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : "Absolute Divorce Act of 2019"
This bill seeks to give opportunity to spouses in irremediably failed marriages to secure an absolute divorce decree under limited grounds and well-defined  judicial procedures to terminate a continuing dysfunction of a long broken marriage; save the children from the pain, stress, and agony consequent to their parents' constant marital clashes and grant the divorce spouses the right to marry again for another chance to achieve marital bliss.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>LAGMAN, EDCEL C.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-07-01</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Belmonte (000 2019-10-08)</td><td>2. Acosta-Alba (000 2020-01-28)</td><tr><td>3. Nieto (000 2020-02-03)</td><td>4. Garcia (P.J.) (000 2020-02-18)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>COMMITEE HEARINGS/ACTIONS:</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp1. Deliberated upon by the Mother Committee on 2020-02-05</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp2. Deliberated by the TWG on 2020-02-12</b><tr><td colspan=3>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp-1st TWG meeting</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp3. Deliberated by the TWG on 2020-03-04</b><tr><td colspan=3>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp-2nd TWG Meeting</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON POPULATION AND FAMILY RELATIONS ON 2019-07-23</td></tr></table>